Second Department,

January, 1947.

(January 13, 1947.) Daniel De Rosa et al., Respondents, v. George C. Tucker et al., Individually and as Trustees under the Will of Arthur C. Tucker, Deceased, Appellants.

Motion for reargument denied, with $10 costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Lewis, P. J., Carswell, Adel, Aid-rich and Holán, JJ. [See ante, p. 835.]
